{"tid":1158361,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"譚耀宗︰中共表態支持修例不算干預本港事務","createTime":"2019-05-17T02:18:32.000Z","updateTime":"2019-05-17T17:31:44.000Z","uid":184679,"like":1,"dislike":41,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"ef0ff6eee5b5a93481fbcc10f7c46d392f046e53","tid":1158361,"uid":184679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-17T02:18:32.000Z","msg":"【Now新聞台】全國人大常委譚耀宗稱，近日中聯辦及港澳辦表態支持港府修訂逃犯條例不算干預本港事務。<br />\n<br />\n譚耀宗又認為，將條例草案直接交付立法會大會審議符合議事規則，而在全體委員會審議階段，議員可以多次發言，亦可以提出修訂，相信議員仍有空間審議草案。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.now.com/home/local/player?newsId=348291&amp;home=1\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fhome%2Flocal%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D348291%26home%3D1&d=2bx9SR3QHfMC8bM4fPAEX%2FSletu%2BpyBbwtETYsduqsw%3D&h=b0f1ffd7\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fhome%2Flocal%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D348291%26home%3D1&h=02cf4358\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.now.com/home/local/player?newsId=348291&amp;home=1</a>"},{"pid":"138465021853e0f3c72872feeb29d8e0a9d4f733","tid":1158361,"uid":33668,"like":27,"dislike":0,"score":27,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-17T02:31:18.000Z","msg":"meanwhile 中口交部鬧緊美國干預中國內政<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7d1cc70b7c88b12919127b24da88bf59c57e8a18","tid":1158361,"uid":33307,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-17T02:32:07.000Z","msg":"咁美國不支持都唔算啦"},{"pid":"6bce4d990c8d061072d86f8b61f94cff0edacf31","tid":1158361,"uid":245033,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-17T02:33:25.000Z","msg":"廢老繼續講廢話<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n今日會見保皇班人都唔會係好事"},{"pid":"40fc72c22e3b1d7f4bcf35db330bfd7a36ccc298","tid":1158361,"uid":48083,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-17T02:33:59.000Z","msg":"比卡超：唔知政府想點樣直接預吿恢復二讀辯論<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1158004\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://li